                <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml ActivityHistorySequenceVi\ntitle 13. Activity History\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nboundary \&quot;ActivityHistory.razor\&quot; as ActivityHistory\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;ActivityLogController\&quot; as ActivityLogController\nentity \&quot;DBContext/ActivityLogs\&quot; as ActivityLogs\n\nActivityHistory -&gt; ApiClient : GetActivityLogsAsync(query)\nactivate ActivityHistory\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; ActivityLogController : GET ActivityLog?page=...&amp;pageSize=...&amp;search=...&amp;action=...&amp;entity=...\nactivate ActivityLogController\n\nActivityLogController -&gt; ActivityLogs : Lấy activity logs theo bộ lọc\nactivate ActivityLogs\nActivityLogs --&gt; ActivityLogController : Dữ liệu activity logs\ndeactivate ActivityLogs\n\nActivityLogController -&gt; ActivityLogs : Phân trang, sắp xếp, map DTO\nactivate ActivityLogs\nActivityLogs --&gt; ActivityLogController : Dữ liệu lịch sử hoạt động\ndeactivate ActivityLogs\n\ndeactivate ActivityLogController\ndeactivate ApiClient\ndeactivate ActivityHistory\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="WZVrMcKF7iwWqCo2LqL2-13">
