                <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml AdminMonitoringSequenceVi\ntitle Theo dõi số lượng khách đang online (Admin)\n\nhide footbox\n\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam sequence {\n  ArrowColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBorderColor #2F4858\n  LifeLineBackgroundColor #EAF3F7\n  ParticipantBorderColor #2F4858\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor white\n  ParticipantFontColor #1F2D3D\n  ActorBorderColor #2F4858\n  ActorBackgroundColor white\n  ActorFontColor #1F2D3D\n}\n\nautonumber 1\n\nactor \&quot;Admin\&quot; as Admin\nboundary \&quot;Giao diện\\n(UsageHistory.razor)\&quot; as UsagePage\ncontrol \&quot;AdminApiClient\&quot; as ApiClient\ncontrol \&quot;UsageController\&quot; as UsageController\ncontrol \&quot;AnalyticsOnlineGuestService\&quot; as PresenceService\nentity \&quot;DBContext\&quot; as DBContext\n\nAdmin -&gt; UsagePage : Mở trang monitoring / Usage History\nactivate UsagePage\n\nUsagePage -&gt; ApiClient : GetUsageHistoryAsync()\nactivate ApiClient\n\nApiClient -&gt; UsageController : GET Usage\nactivate UsageController\n\nUsageController -&gt; DBContext : Lấy dữ liệu usage history\nDBContext --&gt; UsageController : Dữ liệu usage history\ndeactivate DBContext\n\nUsageController -&gt; PresenceService : CountScopedOnlineGuestsAsync(...)\nactivate PresenceService\nPresenceService -&gt; PresenceService : Loại các heartbeat đã hết hạn\nPresenceService --&gt; UsageController : OnlineGuests\ndeactivate PresenceService\n\nUsageController --&gt; ApiClient : UsageHistoryOverviewDto\\n(kèm OnlineGuests)\ndeactivate UsageController\n\nApiClient --&gt; UsagePage : Dữ liệu usage history + OnlineGuests\ndeactivate ApiClient\n\nalt Có khách đang online\n    UsagePage --&gt; Admin : Hiển thị số khách online hiện tại\nelse Không còn heartbeat hợp lệ\n    UsagePage --&gt; Admin : Cập nhật số khách online về 0\nend\n\ndeactivate UsagePage\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="gjlHMqZ_v8curAu2xrZ3-6">
                    <mxCell style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" parent="1" vertex="1">
